title: Casual friendly club
body: Hey guys, i'm just looking for a casual friendly club to play with, and a tag to represent. Not much pressure to play, or be ranked really high, but just some decent people to chat and play with.

replies.body:
Yo! I'm the owner for the club "Anime" with the tag "Anime"
